                MinZ: { type: "int" };
                Name: { default: { type: "string"; value: "" }; type: "string" };
                Preload: { type: "byte" };
            };
            required: [
                "Dimension",
                "IsCircle",
                "MaxX",
                "MaxZ",
                "MinX",
                "MinZ",
                "Name",
            ];
            title: "The TickingArea schema.";
            type: "compound";
        },
        "title"
        | "description",
    > & { description: "The tickingarea data." } & {
        title: "The TickingArea schema.";
    } & { $aliasOf: "TickingArea" };
    VILLAGE_DWELLERS: Omit<
        {
            $fragment: false;
            description: "The village dwellers data.";

                Dwellers: {
                    items: {

                };
            };
